query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `candidateTagAssignments` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `candidateId` int NOT NULL,
  `tagId` int NOT NULL,
  `assignedBy` int NOT NULL,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT (now()),
  CONSTRAINT `candidateTagAssignments_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`),
  CONSTRAINT `candidateTagAssignments_candidateId_fk` FOREIGN KEY (`candidateId`) REFERENCES `candidates`(`id`),
  CONSTRAINT `candidateTagAssignments_tagId_fk` FOREIGN KEY (`tagId`) REFERENCES `candidateTags`(`id`),
  CONSTRAINT `candidateTagAssignments_assignedBy_fk` FOREIGN KEY (`assignedBy`) REFERENCES `users`(`id`)
);
